{"word":"G1251 - διακούομαι - diakoúomai - dee-ak-oo'-om-ahee - Hear","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διακούομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">diakoúomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dee-ak-oo'-om-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Hear</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கேள்"},{"paragraph":"to hear one through, hear to the end, hear with care, hear fully"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Middle voice from <a href=\"#/G1223 - διά - diá - dee-ah'/1223\">G1223</a> and <a href=\"#/G191 - ἀκούω - akoúō - ak-oo'-o/191\">G191</a>; to <i>hear throughout</i>, that is, <i>patiently listen</i> (to a prisoner&rsquo;s plea): - hear.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}